ne'. The correction was considered certain due to the clear semantic improvement and commonality of the correct term. No punctuation stripping was necessary.\n\nPROTOCOL 4 (THE LEMMATIZER): For proper nouns and direct transliterations (e.g., 'ኦኮቻ', 'ኦዌን', 'ኦይሰተር'), the word itself was used as the root. For morphologically derived Amharic words, the base form was identified (e.g., 'ኦዎንታዊ' and 'ኦዘዎቹ' both rooted to 'ኦዞን'; 'ኦዲትሮች' rooted to 'ኦዲት'; 'ኦዲዮው' rooted to 'ኦዲዮ').\n\nPROTOCOL 5 (THE TRANSLATOR): Comprehensive English synonyms were provided, including contextual explanations for proper nouns where relevant (e.g., 'Ogun' as a deity or state).\n\nPROTOCOL 6 (THE GRAMMARIAN): Words were categorized into 'Noun' or 'Adjective' based on their primary function. No morphological details were included in the POS tag.","input_words":["ኦኮቻ","ኦዌን","ኦውል","ኦዎንታዊ","ኦዘዎቹ","ኦዚም","ኦዚን","ኦዝና","ኦዞናማ","ኦዞናይድ","ኦዞዎቹ","ኦይሰተር","ኦዱሎዋ","ኦዱር","ኦዱዱቤ","ኦዲሻ","ኦዲትሮች","ኦዲንባ","ኦዲንጋም","ኦዲየንስ","ኦዲዮው","ኦዲፒም","ኦዲፒን","ኦዴፒ","ኦድርዛንሰኪ","ኦጂት","ኦጆፊዚካ","ኦገስታስ","ኦጉና","ኦጉንዳሬ"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"519e3346-deec-4747-a794-93522eb838ac","created_at":"2026-03-04T08:10:26.019391+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_24/chunk_0616.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦብስተትሪክስ","word":"ኦብስተትሪክስ","synonyms":["obstetrics","midwifery"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦቨም","word":"ኦቨም","synonyms":["ovum","egg cell"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ኦቫሌ","word":"ኦቫሌ","synonyms":["oval","egg-shaped"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦቮንራምዌን","word":"ኦቮንራምዌን","synonyms":["Ovonramwen"],"importance":4},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦቶኖሚ","word":"ኦቶኖሚ","synonyms":["autonomy","self-governance","independence"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦነግ","word":"ኦነጉ","synonyms":["OLF","Oromo Liberation Front"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Adverb","root":"ኦንላይን","word":"ኦንላይንም","synonyms":["online","digitally"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Nou