ntifying acronyms like 'ኦነግ' and 'ኦኤምኤን' from their inflected forms. PROTOCOL 5 (THE TRANSLATOR) provided comprehensive English synonyms. PROTOCOL 6 (THE GRAMMARIAN) assigned high-level parts of speech, classifying loanwords like 'ኦቫሌ' as Adjective and 'ኦንላይን' as Adverb based on typical usage. Scholarly guesses included identifying common acronyms and treating foreign names as proper nouns without further Amharic root analysis.","input_words":["ኦብስ","ኦብስተትሪክስና","ኦቦሊ","ኦቦር","ኦቨም","ኦቫሌ","ኦቮንራምዌን","ኦቮንራምዌንን","ኦቲየኖ","ኦቶኖሚ","ኦች","ኦነጉ","ኦንላይንም","ኦንዬማ","ኦንጃሊ","ኦኖንና","ኦኤምኤንን","ኦኪኪ","ኦካ","ኦካሲዮ","ኦካቻ","ኦኬዚ","ኦክላ","ኦክሰንዴል","ኦክሲቲሊን","ኦክሲቶሲን","ኦክቴቭ","ኦክቶትሮፕ","ኦኮሮን","ኦኮቫንጎ"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"ba9da211-9a9d-4eba-ae54-f1d4e866c803","created_at":"2026-03-04T08:10:47.243563+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_24/chunk_0618.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦጊንጋ","word":"ኦጊንጋ","synonyms":["Oginga"],"importance":3},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦጋ","word":"ኦጋ","synonyms":["Oga"],"importance":3},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦግመንቴሽን","word":"ኦግመንቴሽን","synonyms":["augmentation","increase","enhancement"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦጎኒ","word":"ኦጎኒ","synonyms":["Ogoni"],"importance":3},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ኦፊርም","word":"ኦፊርም","synonyms":["affirm","confirm","assert"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ኦፊርም","word":"ኦፊርንም","synonyms":["affirm (also)","confirm (even)","assert (too)"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ኦፊሳሊያዊ","word":"ኦፊሳሊያዊ","synonyms":["official","formal","authorized"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ኦፊቲክ","word":"ኦፊቲክ","synonyms":["ophitic"],"importance":3},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦፌር","word":"ኦፌር","synonyms":["offer","proposal","bid"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኦፌር","word":"ኦፌርን","synonyms":["offer (object)","proposal (object)","bid (object)"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ኦፌሴላዊ","word":"ኦፌሴላዊ","synonyms":["official","formal","authorized"],"imp